                     <hi rend="largeCaps">GRANT SHEPPARD</hi> (33)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18780114-217-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18780114-217-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18780114-217-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, Stealing an order for the payment of 4<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. of <persName id="t18780114-name-447" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18780114-name-447" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
